message.raw: conversion to uint16 now optional after profiling showed it made things much slower. However it still makes disk write faster. So whether or not it should be done depends on whether our bottleneck is disk write time or data processing time. Conversion to uint16 can be done with a 'uint16' command line argument after the filename
